<c.bg_transparent>to bring us closer to the spheres.</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:06:13.039 --> 00:06:14.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've studied them for some time?</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:06:14.749 --> 00:06:18.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're not here to study the spheres.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We're here to venerate them.</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:06:19.003 --> 00:06:21.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We believe that it is</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>through prayer and meditation</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:06:22.006 --> 00:06:24.133 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>that the Makers become manifest.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:06:24.217 --> 00:06:27.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-The Makers?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-The creator of the spheres.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:06:27.929 --> 00:06:30.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've felt their presence here.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:06:35.686 --> 00:06:37.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're referring to spatial anomalies.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:06:38.272 --> 00:06:39.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Maker's Breath.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:06:39.816 --> 00:06:42.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It reshapes reality,</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:06:42.193 --> 00:06:46.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>allows ordinary men</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a glimpse of the divine.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:06:46.114 --> 00:06:48.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That "Breath" nearly destroyed your ship.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:06:48.449 --> 00:06:50.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, we became careless.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:06:50.827 --> 00:06:54.372 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's easy to do when you're</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the presence of a sphere.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:06:54.455 --> 00:06:57.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're certainly impressive.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:06:57.500 --> 00:06:59.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've found three of them so far.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:06:59.210 --> 00:07:02.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, you're fortunate</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to have such a fast ship.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:07:02.672 --> 00:07:06.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I regret that I'll die having seen</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>only one of the many thousands of spheres.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:07:07.051 --> 00:07:11.431 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Actually, we've determined</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that there are 59 spheres in the expanse.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:07:11.514 --> 00:07:13.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think your estimates are a bit low.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:07:13.724 --> 00:07:15.143 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's doubtful.</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:07:15.893 --> 00:07:17.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>With the Makers, there is no doubt.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:07:18.229 --> 00:07:20.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doubt is the basis</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of all scientific progress.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:07:21.065 --> 00:07:24.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Scientific progress</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has led many people astray.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:07:24.986 --> 00:07:29.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps this is a subject</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we should discuss some other time.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:07:32.243 --> 00:07:33.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I agree, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:07:34.537 --> 00:07:36.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll be glad to know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my engineer believes</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:07:36.706 --> 00:07:38.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that he can repair</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the damage to your vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:07:38.708 --> 00:07:41.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He thinks it shouldn't take</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more than a couple of days.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:07:41.627 --> 00:07:43.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That is good news.</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:07:43.921 --> 00:07:49.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I certainly hope that we'll have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the opportunity to repay your kindness.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:07:57.226 --> 00:08:01.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-May I help you?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'd like to speak with you.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:08:01.981 --> 00:08:03.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is it?</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:08:04.984 --> 00:08:06.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you feeling ill?</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:08:07.653 --> 00:08:11.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wanted to ask you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about a certain procedure.</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:08:11.949 --> 00:08:13.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:08:13.493 --> 00:08:16.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's very difficult for me to talk about.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:08:16.204 --> 00:08:18.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why don't you, uh, have a seat, hmm?</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:08:20.249 --> 00:08:22.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was about to make some Janaran tea.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:08:22.210 --> 00:08:25.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Would you like some?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yes. Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:08:33.221 --> 00:08:35.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Is everyone in place?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:08:35.598 --> 00:08:37.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're just waiting for your signal.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:08:39.810 --> 00:08:41.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You sound hesitant.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:08:43.648 --> 00:08:45.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am sorry, Pri'Nam, but...</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:08:45.608 --> 00:08:48.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you certain</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this is the right thing to do?</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:08:50.863 --> 00:08:54.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you think this ship</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>just came to us by coincidence?</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:08:55.076 --> 00:08:58.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This encounter was clearly</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>ordained by the Makers.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:08:58.371 --> 00:09:00.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But these people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>risked their lives to save us.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:09:00.957 --> 00:09:03.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They desecrated a sphere.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:09:06.754 --> 00:09:08.381 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What we are about to do</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:09:08.464 --> 00:09:11.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>is not just for our salvation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but for theirs as well.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:09:12.969 --> 00:09:14.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know it can be difficult.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:09:14.720 --> 00:09:17.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've been away from home for a long time.</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:09:18.099 --> 00:09:22.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But we have been given the means</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to end the bloodshed once and for all.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:09:22.603 --> 00:09:25.106 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't lose your faith now, Yarrick.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:09:25.940 --> 00:09:27.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Never, Pri'Nam.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:09:32.238 --> 00:09:35.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They believe that godlike beings</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they call the Makers</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:09:36.075 --> 00:09:38.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>created the spheres a thousand years ago.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:09:38.786 --> 00:09:42.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have determined that the spheres</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are nearly a thousand years old.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:09:42.206 --> 00:09:45.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, they also believe that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Makers are using the spheres</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:09:45.710 --> 00:09:48.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to reshape the expanse,</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:09:48.170 --> 00:09:51.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>creating a paradise for when they return.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:09:51.382 --> 00:09:53.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mythology often has a basis in fact.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:09:53.467 --> 00:09:55.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:09:55.094 --> 00:09:56.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come in.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:09:58.347 --> 00:10:00.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Am I disturbing you?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Not at all.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:10:00.725 --> 00:10:02.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excuse me.</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:10:06.397 --> 00:10:09.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I said before that I hoped</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be able to repay your kindness.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:10:09.483 --> 00:10:12.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That isn't necessary.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's already under way.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:10:13.654 --> 00:10:15.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain Archer...</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:10:16.032 --> 00:10:19.619 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You, your crew, this vessel,</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:10:19.702 --> 00:10:22.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>are all about to embark</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on a glorious mission.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:10:23.456 --> 00:10:28.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>At this moment a number of my people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have taken positions around your vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:10:28.544 --> 00:10:32.548 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Their bodies have been equipped</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with powerful organic explosives.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:10:32.632 --> 00:10:35.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>With a single command,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I can order any one of them</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:10:35.426 --> 00:10:37.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to sacrifice their lives.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:10:37.511 --> 00:10:38.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( communicator beeps )</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:10:38.596 --> 00:10:41.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( speaks native language )</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:10:41.766 --> 00:10:44.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( speaking native language )</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:10:53.277 --> 00:10:54.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:11:07.249 --> 00:11:08.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's been an explosion on "C" deck.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:11:08.709 --> 00:11:09.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got a hull breach.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:11:09.960 --> 00:11:13.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Seal off the area. Get security teams--</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Stop.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:11:13.255 --> 00:11:16.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Two of my men are positioned</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>next to your warp reactor.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:11:16.384 --> 00:11:20.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Unless you turn this ship over to me,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll destroy it.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:11:55.381 --> 00:11:57.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He has severe burns!</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:11:57.299 --> 00:11:59.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The other two are suffering</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the effects of rapid decompression!</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:12:00.010 --> 00:12:01.804 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They need immediate medical attention!</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:12:01.887 --> 00:12:05.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My orders are to escort everyone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to their quarters.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:12:05.766 --> 00:12:08.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I will not leave</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>without treating these people.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:12:09.812 --> 00:12:11.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Watch him.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:12:18.737 --> 00:12:20.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER:</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They say they'll destroy </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise.</i></c.bg_transparent>

197
00:12:20.448 --> 00:12:21.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have to believe them.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:12:21.949 --> 00:12:23.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're going along with this.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:12:23.367 --> 00:12:25.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Remember what's at stake,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>why we're out here.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:12:25.327 --> 00:12:26.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Right now we don't have a choice.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:12:26.996 --> 00:12:29.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't take any action against them.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:12:29.540 --> 00:12:31.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that clear?</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:12:31.500 --> 00:12:32.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aye, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:12:34.837 --> 00:12:36.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This isn't over.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:12:39.800 --> 00:12:41.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Make yourself at home.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:12:53.439 --> 00:12:56.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You made the right decision.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:12:56.275 --> 00:12:59.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I promise you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your people won't be harmed.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:13:00.946 --> 00:13:03.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You just murdered one of my people.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:13:05.451 --> 00:13:08.829 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had to erase any doubts</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you might have about our resolve.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:13:10.247 --> 00:13:12.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do you want with my ship?</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:13:12.750 --> 00:13:15.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When I'm satisfied</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the situation is secure,</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:13:15.294 --> 00:13:17.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll answer your questions.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:13:23.969 --> 00:13:27.014 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I also lost a crewman</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in that explosion, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:13:28.807 --> 00:13:31.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll say a prayer for them both.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:13:32.978 --> 00:13:34.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Save your breath.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:13:43.113 --> 00:13:45.658 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Were you given the coordinates</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for Triannon?</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:13:46.742 --> 00:13:48.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Set a course.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:13:48.285 --> 00:13:50.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your highest warp factor.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:13:53.332 --> 00:13:56.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Prepare to fire two of your torpedoes.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:13:56.710 --> 00:13:58.712 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Target my ship's reactor.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:14:02.591 --> 00:14:03.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You heard me.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:14:08.180 --> 00:14:10.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Release the docking clamps.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:14:25.698 --> 00:14:27.575 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opens )</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:14:36.959 --> 00:14:39.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I promised you an explanation.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:14:39.295 --> 00:14:40.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I owe you that.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:14:40.963 --> 00:14:42.882 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where are you taking this ship?</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:14:43.716 --> 00:14:45.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>To my homeworld.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:14:46.260 --> 00:14:48.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be there in three days.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:14:48.304 --> 00:14:51.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For the last century,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a violent group of heretics</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:14:51.891 --> 00:14:53.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>have tried to undermine our way of life.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:14:54.184 --> 00:14:57.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>With your ship, I can deliver</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a final decisive attack.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:14:58.564 --> 00:15:00.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can end this conflict forever.</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:15:00.608 --> 00:15:01.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>War.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:15:03.652 --> 00:15:06.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That was the "glorious mission"</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you were talking about?</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:15:06.989 --> 00:15:08.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm trying to save my people.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:15:08.991 --> 00:15:11.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why do I have the feeling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>these heretics would say the same thing?</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:15:11.911 --> 00:15:13.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They might very well.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:15:14.413 --> 00:15:16.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But it doesn't change what they are.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:15:16.624 --> 00:15:18.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Enemies of the truth.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:15:18.292 --> 00:15:19.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your truth.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:15:19.835 --> 00:15:21.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's only one.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:15:23.422 --> 00:15:26.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How many people do you intend</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to kill with my ship?</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:15:26.383 --> 00:15:27.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughs )</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:15:27.676 --> 00:15:31.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your species is obsessed with numbers.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:15:31.931 --> 00:15:33.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A characteristic of your misguided belief</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:15:34.016 --> 00:15:38.646 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that the secrets of the universe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can be revealed through science.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:15:38.729 --> 00:15:40.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This may sound barbaric to you,</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:15:40.522 --> 00:15:43.067 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but it doesn't matter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how many heretics die.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:15:43.150 --> 00:15:47.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When the Makers return,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>only the faithful will survive.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:15:47.738 --> 00:15:50.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nonbelievers will be swept away.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:15:50.115 --> 00:15:54.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not only Triannons</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but every race within the Chosen Realm.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:15:54.578 --> 00:15:57.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctrines like that make it real easy</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:15:58.082 --> 00:15:59.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to wipe out everyone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who doesn't agree with you.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:16:01.043 --> 00:16:03.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're wrong. It's not easy.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:16:04.046 --> 00:16:07.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If it were, I wouldn't be dreading</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what I have to do next.</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:16:12.304 --> 00:16:14.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've been reviewing your records.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:16:15.099 --> 00:16:18.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've committed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>terrible acts of desecration.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:16:18.644 --> 00:16:22.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not only have you flown within</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the cloaking barrier of three spheres,</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:16:22.523 --> 00:16:25.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you've landed on one and entered another.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:16:26.902 --> 00:16:29.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>For crimes of this magnitude,</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:16:29.154 --> 00:16:33.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>my faith obligates me to destroy your ship</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and put your crew to death.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:16:33.993 --> 00:16:35.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>However...</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:16:37.329 --> 00:16:40.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I cannot ignore the fact</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:16:40.749 --> 00:16:44.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that you put yourselves at risk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to save us.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:16:45.713 --> 00:16:47.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And that I like you, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:16:47.798 --> 00:16:50.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( scoffs )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I believe you're an honorable man.</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:16:52.761 --> 00:16:56.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>So I am going against</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what my faith dictates.</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:16:56.265 --> 00:16:58.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to temper the punishment.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:16:59.852 --> 00:17:01.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As commander of this ship,</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:17:01.603 --> 00:17:04.565 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you may choose one member</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your crew to give up their life.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:17:04.648 --> 00:17:06.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're out of your mind.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:17:06.233 --> 00:17:08.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you won't choose, I'll choose for you.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:17:10.446 --> 00:17:12.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I take no pleasure in this, Captain,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>believe me.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:17:14.658 --> 00:17:16.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I need time to think about this.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:17:17.536 --> 00:17:19.830 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have six hours.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:17:19.913 --> 00:17:23.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I urge you to use this time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to search within yourself</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:17:23.667 --> 00:17:26.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and put these lies out of your mind.</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:17:26.879 --> 00:17:29.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All of this data that you've collected...</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:17:30.924 --> 00:17:34.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Must be erased from existence.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:17:34.845 --> 00:17:35.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:17:43.771 --> 00:17:45.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Six hours, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:18:03.332 --> 00:18:05.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( door opens )</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:18:07.795 --> 00:18:09.838 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>An update on the repairs to your ship.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:18:09.922 --> 00:18:12.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>D'Jamat felt you should be kept apprised.</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:18:12.174 --> 00:18:14.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: That's very considerate of him.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:18:15.052 --> 00:18:16.053 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Wait a minute.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:18:19.389 --> 00:18:22.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Your name's Yarrick, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It is.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:18:23.811 --> 00:18:26.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand your wife</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>paid a visit to sick bay.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:18:27.397 --> 00:18:29.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She had a long talk with my doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:18:29.691 --> 00:18:31.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's pregnant.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:18:32.236 --> 00:18:33.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:18:34.113 --> 00:18:37.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess you also know that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she wants to end the pregnancy.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:18:37.116 --> 00:18:38.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's between her and me.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:18:40.202 --> 00:18:44.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My doctor got the impression</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that she doesn't exactly agree</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:18:44.748 --> 00:18:46.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>with D'Jamat's interpretation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your faith.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:18:47.459 --> 00:18:48.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As a matter of fact,</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:18:49.002 --> 00:18:52.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Phlox said she's grown</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to hate everything about it.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:18:52.714 --> 00:18:53.632 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not true.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:18:53.715 --> 00:18:54.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He also got the impression</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:18:55.008 --> 00:18:57.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that you're not happy with</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the way things are going either.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:18:58.262 --> 00:19:02.015 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>D'Jamat is my spiritual leader.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I will follow him to my death.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:19:02.099 --> 00:19:03.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>From what I've seen,</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:19:03.308 --> 00:19:06.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm pretty sure you're</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>gonna have that opportunity.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:19:16.155 --> 00:19:17.823 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You went to their doctor?</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:19:17.906 --> 00:19:20.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You put us at risk. He told his captain.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:19:20.909 --> 00:19:23.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Does D'Jamat know?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't think so.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:19:25.122 --> 00:19:27.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Did you have the procedure?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:19:27.249 --> 00:19:30.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The doctor said he needed time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to review our physiology.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:19:30.210 --> 00:19:32.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's under guard now. It's too late.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:19:32.504 --> 00:19:34.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's just as well.</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:19:34.339 --> 00:19:35.924 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you changed your mind?</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:19:36.008 --> 00:19:37.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not certain</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's the right thing to do.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:19:37.968 --> 00:19:41.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't watch my son or daughter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>fight in D'Jamat's war.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:19:41.388 --> 00:19:44.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have the ship now.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We'll end the war once and for all.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:19:44.808 --> 00:19:47.728 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't believe that any more than I do.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:19:53.150 --> 00:19:54.735 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Enter.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:19:56.445 --> 00:19:58.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah. I'm glad you've come.</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:20:04.411 --> 00:20:07.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was just looking at your captain's logs.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:20:07.539 --> 00:20:10.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had no idea</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we were such kindred spirits.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:20:10.626 --> 00:20:12.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What makes you think that?</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:20:12.586 --> 00:20:14.546 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know why you're here.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:20:14.630 --> 00:20:17.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>In the... expanse?</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:20:18.175 --> 00:20:20.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It turns out we're both fighting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to save our people.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:20:20.844 --> 00:20:23.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm trying to stop my world</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from being destroyed.</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:20:23.347 --> 00:20:26.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're trying to wipe out everyone</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who doesn't share your beliefs.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:20:27.309 --> 00:20:30.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our situations aren't</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as different as you think.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:20:31.230 --> 00:20:33.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I draw the line</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at murdering innocent people.</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:20:33.565 --> 00:20:35.692 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And not torture?</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:20:36.568 --> 00:20:39.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In your log,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>there is an incident with a prisoner,</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:20:39.279 --> 00:20:41.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>an interrogation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that made use of an airlock.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:20:41.865 --> 00:20:44.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I needed information</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>critical to my mission.</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:20:45.911 --> 00:20:47.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He wasn't hurt.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:20:47.246 --> 00:20:49.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I sympathize with you, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:20:50.374 --> 00:20:52.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've had to make hard choices as well.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:20:53.585 --> 00:20:56.672 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When I was young,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I fought with the holy regiments.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:20:56.755 --> 00:20:59.341 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was commanding a mission.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:20:59.424 --> 00:21:03.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'd infiltrated a village known</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be a heretic stronghold.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:21:04.930 --> 00:21:06.515 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We were instructed to stay concealed</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:21:06.598 --> 00:21:09.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and relay intelligence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about enemy movements.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:21:11.728 --> 00:21:14.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But one of the villagers discovered us.</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:21:15.482 --> 00:21:17.317 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was a small boy.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:21:17.818 --> 00:21:20.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No more than six years old.</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:21:21.947 --> 00:21:25.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We knew if we let him go,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he would alert the village.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:21:27.077 --> 00:21:30.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And if we tried to hold him,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he might give us away.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:21:33.250 --> 00:21:35.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There was only one action to take.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:21:38.630 --> 00:21:40.340 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So I took it.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:21:41.842 --> 00:21:43.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're proud of that.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:21:47.055 --> 00:21:51.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In the service of the Makers,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all actions are blessed ones.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:21:52.019 --> 00:21:53.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are no Makers.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:21:53.937 --> 00:21:55.689 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>At least not how you perceive them.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:21:55.772 --> 00:21:57.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The spheres are machines</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:21:57.316 --> 00:22:00.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>built for a reason</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you and I don't understand.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:22:00.861 --> 00:22:02.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was once like you.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:22:03.864 --> 00:22:05.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But then I felt the Breath.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:22:07.826 --> 00:22:09.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I prayed for you, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:22:09.786 --> 00:22:12.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had hoped that the Makers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would open your eyes to the truth.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:22:13.373 --> 00:22:15.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But it seems that they've turned away.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:22:22.132 --> 00:22:23.717 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You had a choice to make.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:22:24.926 --> 00:22:25.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've made it.</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:22:26.928 --> 00:22:29.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And which crew member have you selected?</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:22:30.015 --> 00:22:31.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've chosen myself.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:22:34.770 --> 00:22:37.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You wanted to kill someone.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:22:37.272 --> 00:22:38.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kill me.</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:22:42.652 --> 00:22:44.362 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I urge you to reconsider.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:22:44.446 --> 00:22:47.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I won't make someone else pay for</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>something that happened under my command.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:22:47.532 --> 00:22:49.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But what about your mission?</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:22:49.493 --> 00:22:52.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When I'm through with your ship,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your crew will need their captain.</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:22:53.163 --> 00:22:54.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pol is a fine commander.</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:22:55.624 --> 00:22:58.001 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are more alike than you think, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:23:01.296 --> 00:23:03.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would make the same choice.</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:23:03.757 --> 00:23:06.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I respect your decision.</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:23:06.134 --> 00:23:08.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then maybe you'll grant a request.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:23:08.303 --> 00:23:10.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is it?</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:23:10.222 --> 00:23:13.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My people have certain customs</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>regarding death.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:23:13.725 --> 00:23:15.936 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's a device on board.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:23:16.019 --> 00:23:18.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We use it to dispose</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of hazardous materials.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:23:19.898 --> 00:23:23.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But on rare occasions,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when the situation arises,</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:23:23.902 --> 00:23:25.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we've also used it for executions.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:23:27.948 --> 00:23:29.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's considered humane.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:23:39.167 --> 00:23:40.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where is this device?</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:23:47.551 --> 00:23:50.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The molecules have been disassembled.</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:23:51.471 --> 00:23:52.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quick and painless.</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:23:56.226 --> 00:23:58.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't change your mind?</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:23:59.771 --> 00:24:01.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No more than I can change yours.</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:24:02.607 --> 00:24:05.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Very well. Proceed.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:24:08.822 --> 00:24:09.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain...</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:24:10.073 --> 00:24:12.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ask Phlox to keep an eye on Porthos.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:24:17.831 --> 00:24:19.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take care of </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise.</i></c.bg_transparent>

389
00:24:29.634 --> 00:24:30.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This won't end here.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:24:44.316 --> 00:24:45.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( inaudible )</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:24:53.700 --> 00:24:55.285 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have my sympathies.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:24:56.328 --> 00:24:59.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You should inform your crew.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They deserve to know.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:25:14.804 --> 00:25:15.972 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've been quiet.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:25:17.599 --> 00:25:19.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm just thinking</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about what's ahead, Pri'Nam.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:25:22.270 --> 00:25:24.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know you too well.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:25:25.899 --> 00:25:27.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me what's wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:25:30.195 --> 00:25:33.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've just begun this mission</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and already three people are dead.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:25:34.074 --> 00:25:36.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-And that bothers you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Shouldn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:25:37.160 --> 00:25:39.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>These people are not our enemy.</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:25:39.246 --> 00:25:43.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They are nonbelievers.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>That makes them our enemy.</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:25:45.001 --> 00:25:46.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:25:49.005 --> 00:25:53.260 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you believe the Makers</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>speak through me?</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:25:54.177 --> 00:25:55.345 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:25:55.428 --> 00:25:58.473 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then when you question me,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you question the Makers.</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:25:59.516 --> 00:26:02.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And there's a word for that.</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:26:02.185 --> 00:26:03.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Heresy.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:26:05.480 --> 00:26:07.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yarrick...</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:26:07.857 --> 00:26:10.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When you begin to sympathize</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the enemy,</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:26:10.944 --> 00:26:13.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you risk becoming the enemy.</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:26:16.992 --> 00:26:18.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:26:59.159 --> 00:27:00.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can I help you?</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:27:10.962 --> 00:27:12.547 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( both grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:27:25.226 --> 00:27:26.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:27:26.644 --> 00:27:28.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Medical scans are against your beliefs.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:27:30.440 --> 00:27:32.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't think the Makers will mind.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:27:35.111 --> 00:27:36.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:27:52.796 --> 00:27:54.422 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( door chimes )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Enter.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:27:55.465 --> 00:27:57.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lyaal is missing. He's not at his station.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:27:57.884 --> 00:27:59.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lyaal.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:28:01.137 --> 00:28:02.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lyaal.</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:28:03.848 --> 00:28:06.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll use the ship's internal sensors</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to find him.</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:28:06.184 --> 00:28:08.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I need to locate one of my men.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:28:10.647 --> 00:28:13.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-We're dropping out of warp.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Main power is being disrupted.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:28:13.608 --> 00:28:14.901 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>From where?</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:28:16.861 --> 00:28:18.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't identify the location.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:28:26.871 --> 00:28:28.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>TUCKER: I'm telling you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I didn't do anything.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:28:28.373 --> 00:28:30.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ask your flunky over here.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:28:30.125 --> 00:28:32.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's been looking over my shoulder</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the whole time.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:28:32.627 --> 00:28:35.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's true. He never left my sight.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:28:37.632 --> 00:28:39.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This did not happen by accident.</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:28:39.759 --> 00:28:41.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pri'Nam, there's something wrong</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:28:41.928 --> 00:28:45.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>with the EPS manifolds on deck "D,"</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>section J-15.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:28:45.265 --> 00:28:47.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yarrick, go with him.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:28:54.566 --> 00:28:56.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's on the left.</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:28:57.485 --> 00:28:58.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You passed it.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:28:59.028 --> 00:29:00.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't want to do that.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:29:01.573 --> 00:29:04.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't win. They'll destroy the ship.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:29:04.784 --> 00:29:06.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not if you help me.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:29:06.619 --> 00:29:08.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:29:08.538 --> 00:29:10.457 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know this is wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:29:10.957 --> 00:29:12.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Everything he's doing.</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:29:13.168 --> 00:29:15.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can put a stop to it, all of it.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:29:15.253 --> 00:29:18.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I won't betray my faith.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Your faith betrayed you.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:29:18.923 --> 00:29:20.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is this really what the Makers want?</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:29:21.009 --> 00:29:23.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To kill people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by the thousands in their name?</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:29:23.845 --> 00:29:26.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that the faith you were raised in?</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:29:27.140 --> 00:29:29.142 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-No.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Then do what's right!</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:29:30.477 --> 00:29:32.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't help me,</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:29:32.729 --> 00:29:35.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you'll be condemning</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your wife and child to death</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:29:35.899 --> 00:29:38.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>because that's how this is going to end.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:29:38.526 --> 00:29:43.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>As long as people like D'Jamat</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dictate what's true and what isn't...</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:29:46.075 --> 00:29:47.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>all you'll ever have is war.</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:29:53.792 --> 00:29:55.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you located Lyaal?</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:29:55.418 --> 00:29:57.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Internal sensors aren't functioning.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:29:57.212 --> 00:29:59.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Systems are down all over the ship.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:29:59.255 --> 00:30:00.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:30:01.591 --> 00:30:02.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is it?</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:30:03.051 --> 00:30:05.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's a convoy of ships approaching.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:30:06.930 --> 00:30:08.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let me see them.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:30:12.310 --> 00:30:16.064 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>These people you're fighting...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what makes them heretics?</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:30:17.190 --> 00:30:21.069 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We believe the Makers created</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Chosen Realm in nine days.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:30:21.152 --> 00:30:22.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They believe it took 10.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:30:23.446 --> 00:30:25.031 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( scoffs )</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:30:25.114 --> 00:30:27.075 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>For that you've been at war</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for over a century?</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:30:29.661 --> 00:30:31.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Found it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What is it?</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:30:32.038 --> 00:30:34.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The environmental controls</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>need to be rerouted to sick bay.</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:30:34.833 --> 00:30:36.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That can only be done from the bridge.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:30:36.251 --> 00:30:37.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm gonna show you how to do it.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:30:38.002 --> 00:30:39.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:30:39.420 --> 00:30:42.131 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dr. Phlox has synthesized</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>an airborne agent.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:30:42.215 --> 00:30:44.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It neutralizes one of the enzymes used</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:30:44.342 --> 00:30:47.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>in the organic explosives,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>renders it inert.</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:30:47.929 --> 00:30:49.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-They're hailing us.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:30:52.684 --> 00:30:53.977 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>D'JAMAT: Surrender now.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:30:54.060 --> 00:30:55.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I have four ships.</i></c.bg_transparent>

476
00:30:55.979 --> 00:30:58.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you had 10 ships,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you wouldn't survive against this vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:30:58.940 --> 00:31:02.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Run your scans.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You'll see that I'm telling the truth.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:31:02.527 --> 00:31:05.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Surrender, and you'll be treated fairly.</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:31:05.363 --> 00:31:07.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>You consider us heretics.</i></c.bg_transparent>

480
00:31:07.448 --> 00:31:10.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We know what you do to them, D'Jamat.</i></c.bg_transparent>

481
00:31:12.996 --> 00:31:15.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Target the lead vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:31:15.540 --> 00:31:16.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do what I say!</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:31:17.125 --> 00:31:18.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:31:24.465 --> 00:31:26.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Prepare to fire torpedoes.</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:31:43.693 --> 00:31:45.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One of the ships has lost engines.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:31:45.528 --> 00:31:46.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Target their main reactor.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:31:50.700 --> 00:31:52.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:32:03.338 --> 00:32:04.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screeching )</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:32:11.220 --> 00:32:12.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't worry. It's harmless.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:32:16.100 --> 00:32:17.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Unless it's agitated.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:32:28.237 --> 00:32:29.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:32:29.989 --> 00:32:33.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have to get to the armory.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We're retaking the ship.</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:32:33.493 --> 00:32:34.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We need the macos.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:32:37.664 --> 00:32:38.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pri'Nam.</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:32:38.831 --> 00:32:40.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's begun.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:32:40.249 --> 00:32:41.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's the status of the engines?</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:32:42.043 --> 00:32:44.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've located the problem.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's under repair.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:32:44.462 --> 00:32:45.505 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( explosion )</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:32:45.588 --> 00:32:48.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The warp reactor should be functioning</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in a few hours.</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:32:48.174 --> 00:32:49.258 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're retreating.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:32:49.342 --> 00:32:51.010 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stay with them.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:32:54.305 --> 00:32:55.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do what I say.</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:33:05.441 --> 00:33:07.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bring us within firing distance.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:33:07.568 --> 00:33:09.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Prepare to lock weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:33:11.322 --> 00:33:12.615 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>PHLOX: Careful!</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:33:12.699 --> 00:33:14.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no antidote for the venom.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:33:14.242 --> 00:33:15.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screeching )</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:33:17.120 --> 00:33:18.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( clicks )</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:33:22.583 --> 00:33:24.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There'll be an extra helping</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of snow beetles</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:33:24.585 --> 00:33:26.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>for you tonight, young lady.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:33:46.524 --> 00:33:48.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAN: Their engines are at maximum.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:33:48.609 --> 00:33:49.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're still gaining.</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:33:50.028 --> 00:33:53.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>D'JAMAT: Good.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We'll eliminate them one by one.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:33:54.741 --> 00:33:55.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:34:24.062 --> 00:34:25.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAN: Hold your fire!</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:34:46.667 --> 00:34:47.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't move.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:34:54.634 --> 00:34:55.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:34:58.554 --> 00:35:00.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're coming into range.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:35:01.557 --> 00:35:02.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lock weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:35:59.448 --> 00:36:00.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( crackles )</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:36:00.950 --> 00:36:02.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:36:36.986 --> 00:36:38.029 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeps )</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:36:41.574 --> 00:36:44.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're sending a transmission.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They want to surrender.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:36:44.744 --> 00:36:45.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Continue firing.</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:36:47.538 --> 00:36:49.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( buzzes )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Weapons aren't functioning.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:36:51.250 --> 00:36:53.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( beeps )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Archer to the bridge.</i></c.bg_transparent>

527
00:36:53.461 --> 00:36:55.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We've rerouted command functions</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to engineering.</i></c.bg_transparent>

528
00:36:55.963 --> 00:36:57.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I've taken weapons off-line.</i></c.bg_transparent>

529
00:36:58.883 --> 00:36:59.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Find him.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:37:01.260 --> 00:37:04.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've also neutralized</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your organic explosives.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:37:04.138 --> 00:37:05.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>D'JAMAT: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>You're lying.</i></c.bg_transparent>

532
00:37:05.431 --> 00:37:07.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go ahead. Try to blow yourself up.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:37:07.600 --> 00:37:08.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I'll wait.</i></c.bg_transparent>

534
00:37:11.062 --> 00:37:13.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand down before anyone else gets hurt.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:37:13.981 --> 00:37:15.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know I won't do that.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:37:15.524 --> 00:37:16.859 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAN: Pri'Nam!</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:37:18.194 --> 00:37:19.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're coming about.</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:37:22.156 --> 00:37:24.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're firing again, Captain!</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:37:25.910 --> 00:37:28.955 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suggest you bring</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your weapons back online!</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:37:35.962 --> 00:37:39.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you willing to sacrifice</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the lives of your crew?</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:37:49.642 --> 00:37:50.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:38:00.569 --> 00:38:01.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( yells )</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:38:12.206 --> 00:38:15.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain, it's Reed. We have the bridge.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:38:17.128 --> 00:38:19.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This would be a lot easier</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if I had weapons back.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:38:19.380 --> 00:38:20.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Stand by.</i></c.bg_transparent>

546
00:38:34.312 --> 00:38:35.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( explosion )</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:38:40.067 --> 00:38:41.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hail them.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:38:46.574 --> 00:38:47.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeps )</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:38:49.035 --> 00:38:50.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is Captain Archer.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:38:52.038 --> 00:38:54.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>D'Jamat is no longer in control</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of this vessel.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:38:55.791 --> 00:38:57.209 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please respond.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:39:01.422 --> 00:39:03.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've retaken the ship.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:39:03.591 --> 00:39:05.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm in command again.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:39:05.259 --> 00:39:07.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Why should I believe you?</i></c.bg_transparent>

555
00:39:07.636 --> 00:39:09.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm powering down my weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:39:14.393 --> 00:39:15.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>See for yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:39:16.729 --> 00:39:18.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:39:26.489 --> 00:39:28.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:39:28.324 --> 00:39:29.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're moving off.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:39:31.786 --> 00:39:33.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:39:47.843 --> 00:39:50.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We just entered orbit around Triannon.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:39:50.513 --> 00:39:51.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's go.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:39:53.516 --> 00:39:56.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've done a terrible thing, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:39:56.894 --> 00:39:59.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've interfered with something</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that was ordained.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:40:00.064 --> 00:40:02.066 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>After centuries of fighting,</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:40:02.149 --> 00:40:04.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was going to bring an end to the war.</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:40:04.360 --> 00:40:05.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We would have had peace.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:40:05.611 --> 00:40:06.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Peace?</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:40:06.904 --> 00:40:09.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>One of my crewmen is dead.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Six others are wounded.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:40:09.198 --> 00:40:11.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-My ship is damaged--</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-None of that is important!</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:40:11.992 --> 00:40:14.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All that matters is the sacred truth.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:40:15.329 --> 00:40:16.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( scoffs )</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:40:16.497 --> 00:40:17.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You want truth?</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:40:19.834 --> 00:40:21.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll show you some truth.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:41:19.268 --> 00:41:22.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>From what we've been able to learn,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this happened eight months ago.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:41:23.105 --> 00:41:25.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Both sides have been decimated.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:41:25.524 --> 00:41:27.818 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are no major cities left.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:41:28.486 --> 00:41:31.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Millions are dead.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:41:34.200 --> 00:41:36.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your faith was going to bring peace.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:41:39.497 --> 00:41:40.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Here it is.</c.bg_transparent>

